company_name: SAATBAU LINZ, OÖ. LANDES-SAATBAUGENOSSENSCHAFT REG. GEN.M.B.H.
information: The company SAATBAU LINZ, OÖ. LANDES-SAATBAUGENOSSENSCHAFT REG. GEN.M.B.H., is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1943, which operates in the Bedding plants, bulbs and seeds industry. It is based in Linz, Austria.
